Author: eren0x
Title: [ANN]ðŸ”¥LIVE ICOðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥ALL-STOCKSðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥GLOBAL STOCK MARKETS REVOLUTION
Body: The All-Stocks Network is a distributed global stock exchange platform which aims to interface with all major stock exchanges and stock brokers around the world. It also allows the trading of crypto tokens backed by real financial assets. The network will create a decentralized system, which will allow all stakeholders trade with its ERC20 standard-compatible token. These backing assets will be held in an escrow account. Moreover, the network will allow users trade in financial assets (such as currencies and bonds) on Blockchain technology. All-Stocks Network will expose generic API interface, giving developers greater capacity to develop their tools and apps for investing, hedging and carrying out transactions using All-Stocks tokens. Well, decentralized organizations that are exposed to cryptocurrency can safeguard their funding through stable assets. While the network will enable investors manage diverse investment portfolios, it will also enable companies issue capitals with ease and flexibility.  They will be successful if they can do what they say.

We will be able to significantly decrease trading fees and commissions, thanks to the trading within the system and there will not be a minimum trading amount. The platform will operate in global and multiple financial areas and markets, and will have a huge trading volume.  The mentioned above, with many more features, will make the project a profitable project that will give the investors good profits for their investment. In addition, AST Tokens will reward Investors with a return on their investment from the future profits of our project's business activity.  Please take a look at our white paper for more information.  We are here for any further question.

Title: [ANN]ðŸ”¥LIVE ICOðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥ALL-STOCKSðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥GLOBAL STOCK MARKETS REVOLUTION
Body: @UpsilonTrooper  Hi, thanks for your reply There are many differences and advantages in our platform, for example:  1. Global trading: AllStocks enables trading in all major markets worldwide within one easy-to-use and automatic platform. 2. Multiple assets including cryptocurrencies: The AllStocks platform supports multiple financial assets such as stocks, bonds, options, and also cryptocurrencies such as Bitcoin and Ethereum. 3. Extremely cheap trading fees and commissions: Because the platform gives priority to trading inside the system, all regular fees and commissions are reduced drastically. 4. Profit sharing: The company will share its profits with AST holders. 5. Huge capacity potential: Because the platform operates in multiple financial areas and markets, it has a potential of immense volumes. The capacity of the global stock markets, for instance, worth $100 trillion alone. 6. Advanced stages of development: The platform is in advanced stages of development. While unfortunately there are many frauds in the ICO field that donâ€™t develop anything, AllStocks already released a live demo before its ICO. Public release is scheduled for the beginning of 2019.  And there are many more... Please check our website

Title: [ANN]ðŸ”¥LIVE ICOðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥ALL-STOCKSðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥GLOBAL STOCK MARKETS REVOLUTION
Body: Hi @negancoin Thank you for your comment. We have three easy steps for trading the backed tokens: 1. Buy AllStocks token, This token will be backed by a real financial asset. the token value will be linked to the real asset he represents. 2. The issued backed token will be ERC20 standard compatible, which means it will be tradable on any crypto exchange platform. while the backed token will be tradeable,  the real asset will be held in a trustee account. 3. The token can be liquefied at any time on our platform, thanks to his backing real asset.  Thanks to a large development team, the platform is in an advanced stage of development. While unfortunately there are many frauds in the ICO field that donâ€™t develop anything, AllStocks already released a live demo before its ICO. Platform public release is scheduled for the beginning of 2019. We welcome you to visit our website and take a glance at the DEMO.  We are here for any further question.

Title: [ANN]ðŸ”¥LIVE ICOðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥ALL-STOCKSðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥GLOBAL STOCK MARKETS REVOLUTION
Body: Our platform will support all ERC20 tokens investors will be able to trade with these tokens as long as they will be registered to trade, most likely that we will begin with the most popular and most tradable tokens.  steps common user will take: 1. send ERC20 tokens to his account on AllStocks. 2. convert to inner-platform Token. 3. Buy backed Tokens that link to a real asset in the real world(it can be stock, bond, future or any other tradable asset. 4. AllStocks will hold this asset in a trusted, transparent, open and regulated manner. The token value will always be matched to real asset value as it can be liquefied at any time. 5. All issued tokens are compatible with ERC20 standard, which means you can trade it anywhere and anytime on all Crypto Exchanges. You can invest in other AllStocks backed token and build your perfect portfolio. Cutting down all middle man fees and broker/banks payments. 6. At any given time, you can liquefy your tokens on AllStocks trading Platform. The platform will then burn the token and transfer the asset or itâ€™s equal market value back to your account. 7. buy, sell, cancel and other trade order will be forward to outer brokerage using the FIX protocol or API.  thanks
